Maneuver with superior control with Werks Traveler™ 4.0. The dual-trolley handle system locks into 3 different positions to accommodate travelers of various heights and easily adjusts when transitioning from pushing the bag to pulling it on two wheels. Lighter. Easier. Better Than Ever. The most popular collection of Victorinox Travel Gear, Werks Traveler 4.0 is now better than ever with dual-caster uprights to accommodate the needs of today's traveler. From the makers of the original Swiss Army Knife.
